h2.underlined Risk Tolerance Questionnaire

p Your first step upon signing up for RetirementPlan.io is to answer a set of questions which will help us to determine your personal risk tolerance.  Your answers are compared to thousands of other people (sourced from the U.S. Federal Reserve) where statistically significant factors are used to extrapolate a potential range of acceptable portfolio volatilities.

p Using the concept of utility (from classical economics) we can mathematically estimate optimal portfolio characteristics from your questionnaire answers.  Members of the optimal set are clearly marked during the portfolio selection process so that you can easily tell if a portfolio may be beyond your willingness/ability to tolerate risk.

p.text-center
  = image_tag "tour/2-questionnaire.png", alt: 'RetirementPlan.io Risk Tolerance Questionnaire screenshot', class: 'img-responsive'

