p RetirementPlan.io is designed to do the hard lifting for you.  Once you have specified the ETFs to use in your portfolio, we provide the exact number of shares to buy to meet your target allocation.  When you go to purchase additional securities (or we note that your portfolio is out of balance), we provide the same information.  All you have to do is purchase the units from your bank or discount brokerage.

h3 No more searching through market quotes and Excel sheets in order to balance your portfolio.

p Initial portfolio setup, quarterly rebalancing, or additional money to invest?  We've got you covered.

